# Screenshots Directory

This directory will contain screenshots of Phoenix Forge for the README.

## Needed Screenshots:
1. main-interface.png - Main device management interface with real-time device detection
2. flash-progress.png - Real-time flashing progress with detailed status updates
3. device-detection.png - Device detection and enumeration
4. firmware-management.png - Firmware search and management interface

## Guidelines:
- Use high-quality screenshots (at least 1920x1080)
- Blur or redact any sensitive information
- Use representative sample data
- Capture the full window with proper lighting/theme
